These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-1::.
3 different pets are kept: frog, goat, hamster
1. the owner of the goat is on the far left##1
2. the owner of the frog is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |     2     |     3     |
| Pet   | goat | hamster | frog |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-2::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, soccer, surfing
1. the person who's sport is surfing is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is climbing is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |   2    |      3       |
| Sport   | climbing | soccer | surfing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-3::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: satire, zombie, horror
1. the person watching satire movies is on the far left##1
2. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |      3      |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | zombie | horror |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-4::.
