1. the person drinking lemonade is on the far right##1
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |
| Beverage   | tea | hot-chocolate | lemonade |

